data.description: Minutes from Ft Stewarts gate 7!! This home has beautiful curb appeal!!! Welcome into the open and bright foyer with newly placed LVP floors throughout main living level. Spacious open floor plan with kitchen overlooking the large living and dining room. Kitchen has lots of cabinets, a pantry and a breakfast bar! Out back you will find an Oasis with white vinyl fence, deck, pergola(S)with an “S”, sheds and the lot is backed up to greenery!! Upstairs you will find 3 spacious bedrooms and a small loft, perfect for an office or study area. The Primary suite has vaulted ceilings and en-suite bathroom and walk-in closet. Across the street you have a playground and green area along with community pool!!
